26
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:40,990
Execute them all!

27
00:01:41,210 --> 00:01:42,910
Please spare me, Your Majesty!

28
00:01:42,990 --> 00:01:44,039
Spare me!

29
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:45,580
Mercy, Your Majesty!

30
00:01:45,590 --> 00:01:46,990
Your lives are spared,

31
