35
00:01:57,440 --> 00:01:59,840
Have the Ministry of Justice
summon Lu Ding.

36
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:02,759
Interrogate him thoroughly.

37
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:03,720
- Yes, Your Majesty.
- Yes, Your Majesty.

38
00:02:03,720 --> 00:02:04,400
Take them away.

39
00:02:04,710 --> 00:02:05,759
Mercy, Your Majesty!

40
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:07,389
I failed to recognize you.

41
00:02:07,390 --> 00:02:08,839
Please spare me!

42
