Uneducated, you say?

63
00:02:53,070 --> 00:02:54,440
What a joke.

64
00:02:54,480 --> 00:02:55,400
You!

65
00:02:58,510 --> 00:02:59,470
Your Majesty,

66
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:01,349
