68
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:04,190
who is better educated.

69
00:03:07,350 --> 00:03:08,270
This way, please.

70
00:03:15,150 --> 00:03:16,070
Your Majesty,

71
00:03:16,160 --> 00:03:18,389
