86
00:03:40,040 --> 00:03:40,960
What do you say?

87
00:03:41,200 --> 00:03:42,039
Sure.

88
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:43,039
If I win,

89
00:03:43,040 --> 00:03:43,960
I won't marry him.

90
00:03:44,070 --> 00:03:44,949
I'll give up.

91
00:03:44,950 --> 00:03:46,320
I don't want to marry you either.

92
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:54,390
Fine.

93
00:04:06,110 --> 00:04:07,480
Until the incense burns out,

94
00:04:07,630 --> 00:04:09,110
