98
00:04:17,950 --> 00:04:19,629
Just recite a Li Bai poem.

99
00:04:19,630 --> 00:04:21,879
That's such a clich├ر
in time-travel dramas.

100
00:04:21,880 --> 00:04:22,999
Besides,

101
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:24,600
