120
00:05:55,110 --> 00:05:57,189
The sky is dim, like an evening drizzle.

121
00:05:57,190 --> 00:06:00,000
I'm waiting for you. As the cooking smoke
drifts, I lift the blind to the rain.

122
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:02,160
Only a window separates us,
